	<item>
		<title>Ironshore Named Oracle Team USA&#8217;s Insurer for 2017 America&#8217;s Cup</title>
		<link>https://www.insurancejournal.com/news/international/2015/10/15/385134.htm</link>
		
				<pubDate>Thu, 15 Oct 2015 09:14:34 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[International & Reinsurance News]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[marine]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Bermuda]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[insurance coverage]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Ironshore Inc.]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.insurancejournal.com/?p=385134</guid>

							<description><![CDATA[Bermuda-based Ironshore Inc. has been named Official Insurer for Oracle Team USA for the 35th America&#8217;s Cup. The announcement said the company will &#8220;provide comprehensive insurance coverage for the team, from the Louis Vuitton America&#8217;s Cup World Series Bermuda regatta, &#8230;]]></description>
		
		
		
